  <name>OpenAir</name>
  <summary>A free and open-source cross-platform podcast app</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      OpenAir is a free and open-source cross-platform podcast app that empowers
      you to explore and enjoy the vast world of podcasts. With a clean,
      intuitive interface, OpenAir makes it easy to discover, subscribe to, and
      listen to your favorite podcasts.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Discover and subscribe to podcasts from anywhere on the internet</li>
      <li>Stream or download episodes for offline listening</li>
      <li>Background playback with media key support</li>
      <li>Customizable playback speed</li>
      <li>Sleep timer for bedtime listening</li>
      <li>OPML import and export</li>
      <li>Sync progress across devices (optional account)</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
